data.description: Welcome home to this well-maintained property! This home offers new flooring and custom faux wood blinds on windows. High-end granite,  all new stainless steel appliances, and recessed lighting throughout. Entertaining options include a fully open floor plan and a lower-level family room in the basement with a wood-burning fireplace. Enter the sizeable, fenced-in backyard with ample space for entertaining. Great location and a short drive to the beltway, shopping, and restaurants.    YOU ARE WARMLY WELCOMED!!
